title: Play Magazine Issue 242 - 2014  UK
description:
Play Magazine Issue 242 - 2014  UK

100 Pages | True PDF | English | 16 MB 


Play has been the voice of PlayStation gaming since 1995, and it has a well-earned reputation for forthright reviews, of getting best and biggest game exclusives and a commitment to high-quality videogames journalism that has seen Play outclass and outlast all of its rivals. Its focus is on PlayStation 3 gaming, bringing its readers all the best PS3 coverage out there, but also offers both an irreverent and intelligent look at all things PlayStation for the discerning PlayStation gamer.
